LORE conclave-history
FLAGS HISTORY
Spirebound Conclave: operated from Cinderteeth Mountains; ran condemned-debtor
labor experiments under sealed administrative warrants from every major city
Mechanism: used Midgaard's arcane registry to reclassify condemned persons
as "arcane material"; bureaucratic atrocity with full institutional cover
Triune seal (Ember, Prism, Pale): on the Kiess obsidian disc and Violet
Compact documentation; connects all five cities to the apparatus
Kowloon: Black Ledger (unredacted founding census with Conclave transfer
names); possibly sealed in undercity cisterns
Midgaard: Unindexed Years ledgers missing; Reckoning faction searching;
Breach Tower believed to hold duplicates
Kiess: founding charter explicitly repudiates sealed warrants from
predecessor authorities — written in direct response to the disc
Rakuen: "resettled south" mechanism — Midgaard removed inconvenient
witnesses; Bloom Council accepted it; Garden Ledger Clerks have not forgiven
~
